OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon says he 'fought hard
OL,4,Cfor patient to have what she wanted'
OL,6,FDisgraced breast surgeon Ian Paterson
OL,7,Ftold an inquest he "fought very hard"
OL,8,Ffor a mother-of-two he operated on to
OL,9,Fhave the treatment she wanted.
OL,11,FThe third of 62 inquests being held
OL,12,Ffor patients of Paterson, who is
OL,13,Fserving a 20-year sentence for
OL,14,Fwounding, has been told Christine
OL,15,FBaker died aged 59 in 2015 after
OL,16,Fputting her trust in his advice to
OL,17,Fhave a "skin-sparing" mastectomy in
OL,18,F2005.
