OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon says he 'fought hard
OL,4,Cfor patient to have what she wanted'
OL,6,FThe hearing has been told secondary
OL,7,Fschool assistant headteacher Mrs
OL,8,FBaker, from Balsall Common, near
OL,9,FSolihull, was advised that there was
OL,10,Fno additional risk to a reconstructive
OL,11,Felement of a "skin-sparing" mastectomy
OL,12,Fin 2005, but saw her cancer return in
OL,13,F2007 and underwent a second mastectomy.
OL,15,FHer husband, Stephen Baker, previously
OL,16,Ftold the inquest that when the cancer
OL,17,Freturned in 2007, Paterson again
OL,18,Fsuggested reconstructive surgery.
