OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon says he 'fought hard
OL,4,Cfor patient to have what she wanted'
OL,6,FHe said the couple were never made
OL,7,Ffully aware that a multi-disciplinary
OL,8,Fteam (MDT) who discussed the case
OL,9,Fbelieved delaying reconstruction until
OL,10,Fafter the second mastectomy was the
OL,11,Fsafest option, and Paterson's
OL,12,Frecommendation had a "higher risk" of
OL,13,Flocal recurrence.
OL,15,FMedics who disagreed with Ian Paterson
OL,16,Fwere 'a bit dysfunctional'
