OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon says he 'fought hard
OL,4,Cfor patient to have what she wanted'
OL,6,FGiving evidence via video link from
OL,7,Fprison on Thursday, Paterson, 66, told
OL,8,FBirmingham and Solihull Coroner's
OL,9,FCourt he remembered the disagreement
OL,10,Fin the MDT.
OL,12,FHe said: "I have got a recollection of
OL,13,Fthis process and how protracted it was
OL,14,Fand how sorry I felt for the patient.
OL,16,F"One of the things this does
OL,17,Fdemonstrate is that I fought very hard
OL,18,Ffor this lady to have what she wanted.
