OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon says he 'fought hard
OL,4,Cfor patient to have what she wanted'
OL,6,F"I was the patient's advocate for what
OL,7,Fshe seemed to want. She had all her
OL,8,Foptions put to her."
OL,10,FAsked by counsel to the inquests
OL,11,FJonathan Jones KC whether he told Mrs
OL,12,FBaker about the disagreement over her
OL,13,Ftreatment options, Paterson said:
OL,14,F"Yes, I'm sure I would have told her."
