OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon says he 'fought hard
OL,4,Cfor patient to have what she wanted'
OL,6,F"If you have done the operation and
OL,7,Fthere's nothing remaining, which is
OL,8,Fwhat you're insinuating, and there
OL,9,Fwasn't ` we know that from subsequent
OL,10,Fpathology ` the weight is the weight.
OL,12,F"Worrying about whether it's too light
OL,13,For too heavy is not going to change
OL,14,Fthe fact the operation was complete."
OL,16,FWhen told that the normal weight for
OL,17,F34B cup breasts is around 350 grams,
OL,18,FPaterson replied: "An average is the
OL,19,Fmiddle part of what is sometimes much
OL,20,Fhigher and sometimes much lower."
