OL,6,FPaterson, originally from Glasgow `
OL,7,Fwho was living in Altrincham in
OL,8,FGreater Manchester when he was tried
OL,9,Fand convicted, was employed by the
OL,10,FHeart of England NHS Foundation Trust
OL,11,Fand practised in the private sector at
OL,12,FSpire Parkway and Spire Little Aston.
OL,14,FHe was appointed as a consultant at
OL,15,FSolihull Hospital in 1998 and
OL,16,Fpractised there until May 2011.
OL,18,FThe inquest continues.
